                            <span data-type="title">Check Your Learning</span>
                            A 50.0-g sample of industrial wastewater was determined to contain 0.48 mg of mercury. Express the mercury concentration of the wastewater in ppm and ppb units.
                          </p>
                          <div data-type="note" id="fs-idm45688384">
                            <h3 class="os-title" data-type="title">
                              <span
                                class="os-title-label"
                                data-type
                                id="[redacted for uniqueness]"
                              >Answer:</span>
                            </h3>
                            <div class="os-note-body">
                              <p id="fs-idm2529904">9.6 ppm, 9600 ppb</p>
                            </div>
